PrecisRe-appointment of LEWIS T. CHAN, of Toronto, Ontario, as a full-time member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Toronto Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years, effective August 31, 2000; and designation of LEWIS T. CHAN as a coordinating member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Toronto Regional Office) for a term of two years.
